 Video Player SDK

Looking to embed videos with advanced playback features? The ImageKit Video Player SDK is a powerful video player built on Video.js with enhanced capabilities like AI-generated subtitles and chapters , shoppable videos, playlists, and more.
 Quick Example

Install the Video Player SDK:
 Copy npm install @imagekit/video-player
 Create a fully-featured video player with just a few lines:
 Copy <!DOCTYPE html>
