 Crop Mode

Let’s now see how crop mode works. We will try the pad_resize crop strategy.
 In this strategy, the output image&#x27;s dimension (height and width) is the same as requested, no cropping occurs, and the aspect ratio is preserved. This is accomplished by adding padding around the output image to get it to match the exact dimension as requested.
